#### [MODIFY] [us-address-service.html](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/us-address-service.html)
Completely rewrite to match the site's native design (using [style.css](file:///Users/tahmidnur/.gemini/antigravity/scratch/theresidentialaddress/style.css), same header/nav/footer, same hero pattern). This page was auto-generated from Stitch and uses Tailwind + a different design language.

